quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,"Inna arsalna noohan ilaqawmihi an anthir qawmaka min qabli an ya/tiyahum AAathabunaleem"
  71,2,"Qala ya qawmi innee lakum natheerunmubeen"
  71,3,"Ani oAAbudoo Allaha wattaqoohuwaateeAAoon"
  71,4,"Yaghfir lakum min thunoobikumwayu-akhkhirkum ila ajalin musamman inna ajala Allahiitha jaa la yu-akhkharu law kuntumtaAAlamoon"
  71,5,"Qala rabbi innee daAAawtu qawmeelaylan wanahara"
  71,6,"Falam yazidhum duAAa-ee illafirara"
  71,7,"Wa-innee kullama daAAawtuhumlitaghfira lahum jaAAaloo asabiAAahum fee athanihimwastaghshaw thiyabahum waasarroo wastakbarooistikbara"
  71,8,"Thumma innee daAAawtuhum jihara"
  71,9,"Thumma innee aAAlantu lahum waasrartu lahumisrara"
  71,10,"Faqultu istaghfiroo rabbakum innahu kanaghaffara"